  -iptables-1.3.5-r1.ebuild:
  Remove stale ebuild.

*iptables-1.3.5-r2 (28 Aug 2007)

  28 Aug 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  iptables-1.3.5-r2.ebuild:
  Do not install /etc/init.d|conf.d stuff, nor /var/lib/iptables,
  for CLIP.

  05 Jul 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  iptables-1.3.5-r1.ebuild:
  Do not give caps through veriexec unless clip-devel is in USE.
  We still give the CLSM privs regardless. That way, execution 
  with needed privs is only possible before reducecap.
  
*iptables-1.3.5-r1 (22 Jan 2007)

  22 Jan 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  iptables-1.3.5-r1.ebuild:
  Initial CLIP import. Add verictl support : CAP_NET_ADMIN+CAP_NET_RAW.
